com.fortyoneconcepts.valjogen.processor.builders

Class TypeBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fortyoneconcepts.valjogen.processor.builders.TypeBuilder

  • final class TypeBuilder
extends Object
    This class assists the ModelBuilder with transforming qualified type names and types in the javax.lang.model.* format to our own valjogen models. Nb: Instances of this class is not multi-thread safe. Create a new for each thread.
